text: Donavon Ferreira (born 21 July 1998) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Northerns in the 2018 Africa T20 Cup on 14 September 2018. He made his List A debut on 19 October 2019, for Northerns in the 2019–20 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Northerns cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
